---
title: Quick Parmesan Chicken Schnitzels & Smokey Aioli with Cherry Tomato Garden Salad & Dijon Dressing
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! We’ve been looking forward to showing off this one. A sharp cheesy crumb coats tender chicken to transform it into the ultimate schnitzel. Add a dollop of smokey aioli for a creamy and flavourful finish.

